<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM4.8">
<l>āva laṉpuṭai yārtam maṉattaṉṟi</l>
<l>mēva laṉvirai cūḻtuva rāpatik</l>
<l>kāva laṉkaṉṟu mēyttu viḷaiyāṭuṅ</l>
<l>kōva laṉvaril kūṭiṭu kūṭalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O circle! [You] be joined if</l>
<l rend="indent">He who cannot dwell in any [place] but in the hearts of</l>
<l rend="indent">people who have great desire and love,</l>
<l rend="indent">the Guardian of the city of Dvārakā surrounded by fragrance,</l>
<l rend="indent">the Cowherd who plays grazing calves</l>
<l>comes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
